name: chilychol
description: Once upon a time, a demon named chol was born. The volcanoes celebrated his arrival and the earth became a sea of fire. The fish left the sea and traveled to the sky with fireballs coming out of their mouths. Each fireball turned in to a star and the fish turned into travelers swimming the galaxies without any destination. Trees drank fires in barren fields, eye and heart and mouth bore fruits as their roots were crying. Chol was hungry and swallowed the fruits have a poison called human.
